        "id": 1172779
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-12-17T22:28:28Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I haven\u0027t found any examples of it not being numeric (or clarification on whether it must be), but Android\u0027s implementation of Build.VERSION.SDK_INT also doesn\u0027t require it to be entirely numeric until P, so I suppose it wouldn\u0027t be that surprising and doing things the way Android does them seems like a good idea.",
